parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the run-flat tire sidewall can cause rapid deflation, loss of control, and accidents, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Bubbles or bulges on the tire sidewall
rapid deflation
vibration while driving
loss of tire pressure
and instability of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Metal Shrapnel in Oil
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of metal shrapnel in the oil can cause catastrophic engine failure, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Engine shutdown
smoke from the engine
knocking or grinding sounds from the engine
oil filter filled with metal shrapnel
excessive oil consumption.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the high pressure fuel pump can cause engine compartment fires, leading to vehicle damage, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Engine shutdown
fire in the engine compartment
warning lights illuminating on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine seizure and stalling can cause loss of control, accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Engine stalling
warning lights illuminating on the dashboard
loss of power
difficulty restarting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine damage, premature wear, and potentially catastrophic engine failure.
symptoms: Excessive oil consumption
oil levels dropping rapidly
warning lights illuminating on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unusual engine noises and failure can cause loss of control, accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Unusual engine noises
knocking or grinding sounds from the engine
warning lights illuminating on the dashboard
engine failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine overheating can cause engine damage, premature wear, and potentially catastrophic engine failure.
symptoms: Engine overheating
warning lights illuminating on the dashboard
reduced engine power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A failed low-pressure fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The fuel supply warning sign appears
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle hesitates or jerks while accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A drivetrain malfunction can cause the vehicle to shake, hesitate, or lose power while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shakes or vibrates while driving
the drivetrain malfunction error message appears
the vehicle hesitates or jerks while accelerating
the vehicle loses power or stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience electrical device shutdowns, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The "increased battery discharge" and "all electrical devices will shut off" warning messages appear
the vehicle stalls or loses power
electrical devices shut down
the vehicle smells like burning wires or smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power and momentum, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls unexpectedly
often while driving at high speeds
with messages such as "Drive-train malfunction
no maximum output
drive moderately" or "Automatic start/stop deactivated: engine will not start automatically. Press the start/stop button to start the engine."

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and momentum, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences erratic shifting
hesitation
and stalling
making it difficult to control the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to repair recalled airbag and power train components can lead to serious safety risks, including injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts for recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of a tire can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and potentially causing injury or death.
symptoms: The tire develops a bubble on the sidewall
which can cause the tire to shred
leading to a loss of control.
